name: Via Ferrata Foradada del Toscar
description:
Introduction

A nice via ferrata just outside of the town of Samper, Spain. Look for a sculpture on the right of the road with giant spears, then a little further on the road to the left is the parking area with a large via ferrata information sign. Parking area: 42.4159, 0.3345
